\par
Hi b\u7841?n, th\u7853?t vui khi b\u7841?n \f1\'f0\f2\u7871?n v\u7899?i Project c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh, \b\f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7885?c qua c\f0\lang1033\'e1i n\'e0y m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t l\f0\lang1033\'fac \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7875? hi\u7875?u t\u7841?i sao l\u7841?i c\f0\lang1033\'f3 n\'f3, n\'f3 s\f2\lang1066\u7869? l\f0\lang1033\'e0m \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c vi\u7879?c g\f0\lang1033\'ec v\'e0 t\f2\lang1066\u7841?i sao m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh l\f2\lang1066\u7841?i \f1\'f0\f2\u7847?u t\f1\u432? th\f2\u7901?i gian v\f0\lang1033\'e0o n\'f3 nh\f1\u432? v\f2\lang1066\u7853?y nh\f0\lang1033\'e9.\b0\par
\par
Tr\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7899?c ti\f0\lang1033\'ean gi\f2\lang1066\u7889?ng nh\f1\u432? bao l\f2\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh vi\'ean kh\'e1c \f2\lang1066\u7903? Vi\u7879?t Nam , m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh c\f1\u361?ng b\f2\lang1066\u7855?t \f1\'f0\f2\u7847?u l\f0\lang1033\'e0m vi\f2\lang1066\u7879?c trong ngh\u7873? l\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh n\'e0y \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c 10 n\f1\'e3m r\f2\u7891?i, c\f1\u361?ng t\f2\u7915?ng qua kha kh\f0\lang1033\'e1 c\'e1c c\'f4ng ty v\'e0 kha kh\'e1 c\'e1c d\f2\lang1066\u7921? \f0\lang1033\'e1n kh\'e1c nhau. M\'ecnh xin n\'f3i l\'e0 m\'ecnh l\'e0 l\f2\lang1066\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh vi\'ean nh\'e9, kh\'f4ng li\'ean quan g\'ec \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7871?n RANK n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\f2\lang1066\u7843? TECH,ARCHITECT, SENIOR .v.v.v. M\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\f2\lang1066\u7845?y chia rank nh\f1\u432? v\f2\u7853?y l\f0\lang1033\'e0m cho m\f2\lang1066\u7885?i ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i t\f1\u432?\f2\u7903?ng t\f1\u432?\f2\u7903?ng \f1\'f0\f2\u7871?n nh\u7919?ng nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n v\f2\lang1066\u7853?t trong truy\u7879?n Kim Dung . Nh\u7919?ng nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n v\f2\lang1066\u7853?t m\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\f2\lang1066\u7869? luy\u7879?n m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh c\'f9ng c\f2\lang1066\u7921?c \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? tr\u7903? th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7841?i cao th\u7911? trong m\f0\lang1033\'f4n ph\'e1i n\'e0o \f1\'f0\f0\'f3. M\'ecnh kh\'f4ng ph\f2\lang1066\u7843?i l\f0\lang1033\'e0 ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i nh\f1\u432? v\f2\u7853?y, m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh cho r\f2\lang1066\u7857?ng nh\u7919?ng nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n v\f2\lang1066\u7853?t nh\f1\u432? v\f2\u7853?y ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? gi\u7843?i tr\f0\lang1033\'ed, kh\'f4ng th\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f0\lang1033\'e1p d\f2\lang1066\u7909?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0o \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7901?i s\u7889?ng th\u7921?c. \f1\'d0\f2\u7863?c bi\u7879?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 l\'e0m m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t DEV y\f0\lang1033\'eau ngh\f2\lang1066\u7873?\f0\lang1033  \f2\lang1066 th\f0\lang1033\'ec vi\f2\lang1066\u7879?c chia rank nh\f1\u432? v\f2\u7853?y s\u7869? l\f0\lang1033\'e0m cho b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\'f2n ch\f1\'e3m ch\f0\'fa v\'e0o d\'f2ng code n\f2\lang1066\u7919?a. \f0\lang1033\'dd ki\f2\lang1066\u7871?n c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh l\'e0 nh\f1\u432? th\f2\lang1066\u7871? n\f0\lang1033\'ean n\f2\lang1066\u7871?u b\u7841?n n\f0\lang1033\'e0o th\f2\lang1066\u7845?y c\f0\lang1033\'e1i vi\f2\lang1066\u7879?c m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh gi\f2\lang1066\u7899?i thi\u7879?u m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh l\'e0  m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t DEV kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ph\'f9 h\f2\lang1066\u7907?p \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? chia s\u7867? v\u7899?i v\u7883? tr\f0\lang1033\'ed c\'e1c b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n \f1\'f0ang c\f0\lang1033\'f3 trong c\'f4ng ty th\'ec c\'e1c b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng xem n\f2\lang1066\u7919?a, m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh t\'f4n tr\f2\lang1066\u7885?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1c b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n.\par
\par
Okie , nh\f1\u432? m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh \f1\'f0\f0\'e3 n\'f3i m\'ecnh l\'e0m dev g\f2\lang1066\u7847?n 10 n\f1\'e3m r\f2\u7891?i, qua nhi\u7873?u c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ty r\f2\lang1066\u7891?i, n\f0\lang1033\'ean m\'ecnh c\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? kh\f0\lang1033\'e1 t\f2\lang1066\u7921? tin n\f0\lang1033\'f3i r\f2\lang1066\u7857?ng m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh t\'edch l\f1\u361?y \'f0\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c m\u7897?t s\u7889? kinh nghi\u7879?m nh\u7845?t \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh trong\f0\lang1033  \f2\lang1066 qu\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\'ecnh t\f2\lang1066\u7841?o ra c\f0\lang1033\'e1c s\f2\lang1066\u7843?n ph\u7849?m , c\f0\lang1033\'e1c d\f2\lang1066\u7883?ch v\u7909? trong ng\f0\lang1033\'e0nh ngh\f2\lang1066\u7873? n\f0\lang1033\'e0y. V\'e0 b\f2\lang1066\u7895?ng nhi\f0\lang1033\'ean m\'ecnh th\f2\lang1066\u7845?y r\u7857?ng m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh gi\'e0 \f1\'f0i, kh\f0\'f4ng c\'f2n s\f2\lang1066\u7913?c l\f0\lang1033\'e0m vi\f2\lang1066\u7879?c tr\f0\lang1033\'e2u b\'f2 n\f2\lang1066\u7919?a. M\f0\lang1033\'ecnh m\f2\lang1066\u7845?t ni\u7873?m tin v\f0\lang1033\'e0o nh\f2\lang1066\u7919?ng d\f0\lang1033\'f2ng code \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7865?p nh\f1\u432? m\u417? v\f0\lang1033\'ec nh\f2\lang1066\u7919?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1i v\f2\lang1066\u7909?n v\u7863?t nh\f1\u432? c\u417?m \f0\lang1033\'e1o g\f2\lang1066\u7841?o ti\u7873?n h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ng\'e0y. \b Nh\f1\u432?ng b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n bi\u7871?t kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng, 10 n\f1\'e3m t\f0\'edch l\f1\u361?y m\f0\'e0 l\f2\lang1066\u7841?i v\u7845?t kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng n\'f3 \f1\'f0i th\f0\'ec ph\'ed qu\'e1, ch\'ed \'edt m\'ecnh c\f1\u361?ng ph\f2\lang1066\u7843?i \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? l\u7841?i cho m\u7885?i ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i m\u7897?t c\f0\lang1033\'e1i g\'ec \f1\'f0\f0\'f3 ch\f2\lang1066\u7913?? \b0 V\u7899?i t\f1\u432? t\u432?\f2\u7903?ng nh\f1\u432? v\f2\u7853?y n\f0\lang1033\'ean m\'ecnh quy\f2\lang1066\u7871?t \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh s\u7869? t\u7841?o ra m\u7897?t s\u7843?n ph\u7849?m v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f1\'f0\u432?a nh\f2\lang1066\u7919?ng g\f0\lang1033\'ec t\f2\lang1066\u7889?t nh\u7845?t m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh bi\f2\lang1066\u7871?t, nh\u7919?ng g\f0\lang1033\'ec m\'ecnh h\f2\lang1066\u7885?c \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c t\u7915? nh\u7919?ng ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i \f1\'f0\f2\u7847?u ti\f0\lang1033\'ean d\'ecu d\f2\lang1066\u7855?t m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh v\'e0o ngh\f2\lang1066\u7873?, t\u7915? \f1\'f0\f2\u7891?ng nghi\u7879?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0 t\f2\lang1066\u7915? nh\u7919?ng chuy\f0\lang1033\'ean gia bi\f2\lang1066\u7871?t t\f0\lang1033\'ean nh\f1\u432?ng ch\u432?a m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t l\u7847?n g\u7863?p m\u7863?t tr\f0\lang1033\'ean c\'e1c di\f2\lang1066\u7877?n d\f0\lang1033\'e0n, trang web c\'e1 nh\'e2n blog .v.v.v. v\'e0o n\'f3.\par
